A collection of short php/perl/shell scripts 

- ssh-bruteforce-notify -- notifies abuse contact for IP network which tries to brute-force your FreeBSD SSH server

- dyn-update -- uses nsupdate utility for dyndns.org-style DNS updates with keys

- domain-add -- script to add new DNS zone files

- facebook_realtime - script to register with, check on and delete subscription to Facebook Realtime API
    - ex: Show current subscriptions:  php facebook_realtime_register.php -i <app_id> -s <app_secret> -a get
    - ex: Register for feed updates: php facebook_realtime_register.php -i <app_id> -s <app_secret> -c http://mysite.com/facebook_callback.php -t <verify_token> -a post -f feed
    - ex: Delete all subscriptions:  php facebook_realtime_register.php -i <app_id> -s <app_secret> -a delete
